---
/**
 * AITyping — three dots that bounce while the AI is "thinking".
 *
 * Pure CSS animation via the `bounce-dot` keyframe with staggered delays
 * (0 / 150ms / 300ms). The cycler in AIChat injects this markup imperatively;
 * this file documents the intended DOM and stays available as a component.
 */
---

<div class="self-start bg-paper px-3.5 py-2.5 rounded-3.5 rounded-bl-sm inline-flex gap-1">
  <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-text-mute" style="animation:bounce-dot 1.2s infinite;"></span>
  <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-text-mute" style="animation:bounce-dot 1.2s infinite 0.15s;"></span>
  <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-text-mute" style="animation:bounce-dot 1.2s infinite 0.3s;"></span>
</div>
